---
description: Project conventions for this React/Vite/TanStack starter
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow the conventions in [AGENTS.md](mdc:AGENTS.md) — it is the canonical
instructions file for this repository.

Key points:

- Use `bun` / `bunx`, never `npm` / `npx`.
- Run `bun run verify` (lint + typecheck + format + test + build) before
  considering any change complete.
- All new features require tests (Vitest + Testing Library, co-located).
- `src/routeTree.gen.ts` is generated by TanStack Router — never edit by hand.
- Only stage files related to the current task; never force push.
